svg.title: F What if..
svg.text: ... Fauske became the global top training and education center for fish preparation and cooking for high class cooks?
... Fauske became one of the most important biotechnological sup-pliers for Aquaculture in Northern Norway?

... Tourists would not only pass through but stay in Fauske becau-se they want to experience the freshest salmon in the world in a local fish restaurant at the wate-front or at the local fresh fish market in the city center?
... AMFI got more tenants, which sell salmon and salmon products?
... Aquaculture products would be distributed through the goods distribution center Fauske via railway, the E6 and the Fasuke harbour?
... Fauske had a fish processing factory?
... and Fauske would be very proud of it and would be more active and share its specialities in global exhibitions and on the internet?
